We try to collect proposed amendments to directive texts.  Amendments are written at the demand of legislators at various occasions.  For many people, writing amendments is a learning exercise.

== News & Chronology ==
 * 2005-04-19 [[http://codeliberty.org/amends/noprogs.html|Beauprez: Enhanced 'no programs' clause]]  
 * 2004-11-24 jheald amendments (ver 0.3)
 * 2004-11-23 [[http://www.codeliberty.org/dd2.html|Beauprez amendment]] [[http://www.codeliberty.org/dd2.pdf|(PDF)]] and [[http://codeliberty.org/explanation.php|Explanation]]
 * 2004-06-00 Kaindl minimal amendments to Council
 * 2003 gibuskro collects all official amendments in [[AmendDbEn| amend database]] on [[GenbaEn| genba]]
 * 2002-2003 [[EubsaPropEn| FFII Counter-Proposal to EP Directive]]
